Description: Containing by weight 99.99 percent or more of zinc
Containing by weight less than 99.99 percent of zinc:
Zinc bars, rods, profiles and wire
Zinc plates, sheets, strip and foil
Articles of a type used for household, table or kitchen use; toilet and sanitary wares; all the foregoing and parts thereof of zinc
Zinc tubes, pipes and tube or pipe fittings (for example, couplings, elbows, sleeves)
